    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITED\nMENU",
      "Anytime à-la-carte\nin-flight snack\nWe will be pleased to bring you the following\nitems anytime after the first meal service,\nand until 90 minutes prior to landing.\nSimply notify one of your flight attendants.\nChilled deli plate\nServed with a warm roll\nHäagen-Dazs. raspberry sorbet\nFruit and yogurt parfait\nFresh whole fruit\nAvailable near the galley; please help yourself\nA selection of gourmet snacks and sweets\nAvailable at the front of the cabin or near the galley;\nplease help yourself\nFirst\nUSA-NRT\nAnytime a la carte card\n4105002"
    ],
